{"tid":1421064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"八月尾嚟場百萬遊行 九月再嚟多次大三罷","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:11:27.000Z","uid":198146,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c24c3fc7880d0adcadd0f9c41e7e33207bbbf3","tid":1421064,"uid":198146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n尋日我哋85三罷無可否認係成功嘅<br />\n尋日每區嘅手足都真係搞得好好睇睇<br />\n心酸嘅係 警察依家只係越嚟越癲喪<br />\n落街行過都亂捉亂嚇人<br />\nbetween 多謝好多巴絲睇完我個post<br />\n都入咗嚟荃灣一齊be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋呢場運動<br />\n要繼續進行嘅時候<br />\n大家一定要方向正確<br />\n林鄭繼續嘅兜圈 <br />\n繼續攞班狗嚟做condom同政治洗腦<br />\n我哋就更加唔好俾中共同班三毛帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我喺呢度強烈建議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">八月尾</span><br />\n推大型港島和理非遊行</span><br />\n話俾香港人 話俾全世界聽<br />\n我哋嘅訴求 對警隊嘅執法同濫權不滿<br />\n我哋未玩完 我哋唔會咁輕易就屈服喺<br />\n<strong>呢個反智嘅政權下</strong><br />\n<br />\n而我認為昨日籌備咗咁耐嘅三罷活動<br />\n可以趁開學季節 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺<span style=\"color: red;\">九月</span>嚟多次大三罷</span><br />\n正正式式三罷 罷工 罷市 同 <strong>罷埋課</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好希望大家一齊集思廣益<br />\n喺呢個時勢<br />\n我哋唔好再亂分化話前線玩權力遊戲<br />\n我自己係一個前線<br />\n係因為出耐咗而越走越前<br />\n我哋好容易會激動<br />\n因為我哋好想大家每次都安全離開<br />\n香港人最近都好大壓力<br />\n可能會激動咗啲 <br />\n但大家出到嚟都係想一條心 we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ee1c6a6b1e0455a5a622dfb13c3a78440d2e43f","tid":1421064,"uid":198146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1df77dc15b8539c444fd564bc7ae75e657623cb","tid":1421064,"uid":198146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0cfbddcb43512700965b65a6fbb72a9db37e69","tid":1421064,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:04:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"af3a16d4363e10a7c76b94f0aebd1fc9e1763f36","tid":1421064,"uid":198146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}